/*
  Treadmill Controller with Manual Button Controls
  Based on the original bep_code.ino

  Features:
  - Start/Stop buttons
  - Speed increase/decrease buttons (0.1 km/h increments)
  - Serial communication with treadmill
  - Speed range: 0.5 - 20.0 km/h
  - LCD display showing current status

  Button connections:
  - Pin 3: Start button (with pull-up resistor)
  - Pin 4: Stop button (with pull-up resistor)
  - Pin 5: Speed Up button (with pull-up resistor)
  - Pin 6: Speed Down button (with pull-up resistor)

  LCD connections (16x2):
  - VSS to ground
  - VDD to 5V
  - V0 to potentiometer (contrast)
  - RS to digital pin 12
  - Enable to digital pin 11
  - D4 to digital pin 10
  - D5 to digital pin 9
  - D6 to digital pin 8
  - D7 to digital pin 7
  - A to 5V (backlight)
  - K to ground (backlight)
*/

